description: Perfectly situated between Buckhead and Midtown, this spacious 1-bedroom, 1-bath Mid-Century Condo features a large, open living area filled with natural light from floor-to-ceiling windows. A bright sunroom offers the perfect spot for a home office or workout space. Secured gated parking, and ample visitor spaces, pool, and tennis courts—all in a serene, tranquil setting. Offering the perfect blend of city living with a peaceful setting, within walking distance of Beltline, shops & restaurants.
